      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly start? This vehicle is in poor condition and will definitely need some mechanical and cosmetic TLC to get it back to its best. It's an honest fixer-upper with great potential for someone handy or looking for a parts car\u2014bring your tools and your vision to give this one a second life!",
