    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading on the hood, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and a few cracked trim pieces. Mechanically, it starts and runs consistently, but it will likely need some suspension work and a new set of tires in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character and routine upcoming maintenance.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
